c: 58
v: 2
t: "Iwo amene ali pakati panu ndipo amasudzula akazi awo ponena kuti: “Iwe uli ngati msana wa Amai anga.” Iwo sangakhale Amai awo ai. Palibe amene angakhale amayi awo, kupatula okhawo amene anawabara. Ndithudi iwo amalankhula mau oipa ndi bodza. Ndithudi Mulungu amakhululukira nthawi zonse"